definition.text: Now we are ready to push your new profile to the main Superalgos repository!

paragraphs.text: If you have gone through the welcome tutorials already, you should have set up your GitHub authentication and submitted a review. Submitting your profile will be exactly the same. Easy right!
If this sounds strange to you. Read the docs page open to the right and go through the steps to set up your GitHub authentication. Then come back here and we'll finish up!
